{"_path":"/maps/_web/browser/browser-engine","_dir":"browser","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"浏览器引擎","description":"Web 浏览器引擎相关知识，包括主流引擎和新兴引擎项目","original_path":"content/6.maps/_web/browser/browser-engine.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"chrome-早期团队回忆录"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Chrome 早期团队回忆录"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Evan Martin（Ninja 构建系统作者）回忆 2007-2012 年在 Chrome 团队的经历：\nGoogle 做 Chrome 的动机是\"让 Web 成功\"，早期成功源于罕见的 alignment 和人才密度。\nOld Google 比今天的 Google 更尊重员工。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://neugierig.org/software/blog/2022/12/chrome.html","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Chrome, 10 years later"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"ladybird-是什么"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ladybird 是什么？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ladybird 是一个从零构建的全新浏览器引擎，"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"非任何现有浏览器的分支"}]},{"type":"text","value":"（Not a fork）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"项目由 501(c)(3) 非营利组织支持，致力于解决\"整个网络仅由少数几家有自身议程的公司控制的浏览器引擎驱动\"的问题。目前网络主要由 Blink（Chrome）、WebKit（Safari）和 Gecko（Firefox）三大引擎主导。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ladybird.org/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ladybird 官网"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"ladybird-的技术特点"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ladybird 的技术特点"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"完全独立"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：不使用 Blink、WebKit、Gecko 等现有引擎的任何代码，基于 Web 标准全新构建。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"语言演进"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：原基于 C++，2026 年 2 月宣布采用 Rust 作为 C++ 的继任语言，并使用 AI 代理加速迁移。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"单一专注"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：专注于一件事——构建 Web 浏览器，拒绝功能蔓延。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ladybird.org/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ladybird 官网"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"ladybird-的运营模式"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ladybird 的运营模式"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"无用户变现"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：拒绝默认搜索协议、加密代币等模式，完全依赖捐赠和赞助。主要赞助商包括 FUTO、Shopify、Cloudflare 等。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"团队组织"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：8 名全职付费工程师 + 大量社区志愿者，保持 18 个月资金储备。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"路线图"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：2026 年发布 Linux/macOS Alpha 版（面向开发者和早期用户）；Windows 和移动端非当前优先。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://ladybird.org/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Ladybird 官网"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_web:browser:browser-engine.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_web/browser/browser-engine.md","_stem":"6.maps/_web/browser/browser-engine","_extension":"md"}